# Summary
This documentation details the Amplitude Data integration with Planhat, allowing real-time streaming of events as User Activities to Planhat's customer platform. The integration matches Amplitude user_id to Planhat's externalId, requires admin access to a paid Planhat plan, and supports sending all user, event, and group properties with configurable filters.

